<p>I sincerely enjoyed it a lot, because I hate these URLs polluted by social media, especially those on Facebook. And I also liked the Neat URL because it did not interfere with anything in the functioning or the speed of Firefox, it remains fast, as always! ‚úå) But if you don‚Äôt like it, just remove it through the same Extensions panel ‚Üí ‚óè‚óè‚óè ‚Üí remove.</p>

